                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-392-off2018 t18310908-392-crimeloc2021"></join>. On the afternoon of the 29th of August the prisoner came and asked to look at some black silk handkerchiefs, which were shown to him; he spread them on the counter, took from under them two handkerchiefs, and put them into his left-hand pocket - I seized him; he pulled them out of his pocket, and threw them behind him - he begged we would do nothing to him, and said these were hard times.</p>
